Love is a conveyor

entered to a plenum;

crypts of a mind

fill to alms of bends.

2020.03



Ironic that it happened

in a room full of mirrors;

my conscience telling me
to not let myself astray.

and so I refrained,
and did not look -

2020.04.12



Count more the days you

felt infinite in your work

rather than at odds with it

2020.04.16


